Queenie Leonard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Queenie_Leonard 0 Queenie Leonard (18 February 1905 – 17 January 2002) was an English character actress and singer. She was the last surviving cast member of And Then There Were None (1945). Queenie_Leonard ( 18_February_1905 – 17_January_2002 ) was an_English_character_actress_and_singer . She was the_last_surviving_cast_member of And Then There Were None_(_1945_) .
